flowchart LR
    Client([Client])
    TweetSvc[Tweet Service]
    TweetsDB[(Tweets Store<br/>wide-column,<br/>partition by author)]
    FanOut[Fan-out Service<br/>push if &lt;10k followers<br/>skip for celebs]
    Timelines[(Home Timeline Cache<br/>sorted-set per user)]
    TimelineSvc[Timeline Service<br/>merge push + pull-celebs<br/>+ ML rank]
    SearchIdx[(Search Index<br/>time-partitioned)]
    Trending[Trending Pipeline<br/>stream processor top-K]

    Client -->|post| TweetSvc
    TweetSvc --> TweetsDB
    TweetSvc --> FanOut
    FanOut -->|push| Timelines
    TweetSvc -.->|event stream| SearchIdx
    TweetSvc -.->|event stream| Trending
    Client -->|read feed| TimelineSvc
    TimelineSvc -->|push-built| Timelines
    TimelineSvc -->|pull celebs| TweetsDB

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Client external
    class TweetSvc,FanOut,TimelineSvc,Trending service
